	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I don't advise using the method to casting as sometimes something will resist and then the whole thing is kaput.<br><br>It's important to note what order your spells are in as you will be using the number of that spell in the Social you will be creating.<br><br>So if you have:<br><br>1 Root<br>2 Sicken<br>3 Tainted Breath<br>4 and so on<br><br>you would need the make a social with the following text.<br><br>/cast 1<br>/pause 22<br>/cast 2<br>/pause 20<br>/cast 3<br><br>The numbers after the /pause are the casting time for the spell plus a small amount for server trip time in tenths of a second.<br><br>If something gets resisted of or fiz.&nbsp;&nbsp;It will continue to cast spells without abandon.<br><br>Hope that helps<br><br>Racknar Icerunner<br>Barbarian Shaman of the 22 Rite<br>Blackwatch Guards<br>Zeb<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
