	   <tr><td colspan=2>Okay, here's my advice:<br><br>You're probably way KoS in all parts of Freeport.&nbsp;&nbsp;So here's what you do:  Get in on a couple of Lucan raids.  At level 50, you are certainly of sufficient level to do this.  Helping to kill Lucan (who is Freeport Militia) only lowers West and East Freeport faction.  Also, killing Lucan RAISES your faction in North Freeport.  Tthe pally guards in North Freeport just looove people who whoop ass on Lucan.   After a few raids on Lucan, you just might be non-KoS in North Freeport.<br><br>note:  Lucan is extremely magic resistant (if not 100% MR), so in order to get some of the faction hits, all you need to do is throw a heal to a single tank fighting him.  Trying to dot or nuke is just a waste of your mana.<br>&nbsp;<br>Badjur<br>54 Barbarian Shaman (Druzzil Ro)<br><br>Aepox Weeblatter<br>35 Dwarf Warrior</td></tr>
